                    <ul>
						<li>Add an empty &lt;div&gt; tag in the body of the html file. The id of this &lt;div&gt; must match the id that you used in the Javascript fragment given above.</li>
						<li>Example:<br />
<pre>&lt;body&gt;	
	&lt;div id="phen_vis"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;body&gt;</pre>						
						</li>
					</ul>										
				</div><br />
				
</div>
